data.description: Explore the charm of Sandpoint living with this incredible opportunity—the most budget-friendly three-bedroom residence within the city limits. This bright 3-bedroom, 2.5-bath townhome spans 1241 sq ft., providing ample space for comfortable living. Step onto a covered patio overlooking the backyard, a perfect spot for morning coffee. Enjoy the luxury of a 2-car attached garage with cabinets and a workbench, providing practical storage solutions. Revel in the proximity to downtown, city beach, Sand Creek trail system, and the renowned Schweitzer Mountain Resort. Seize the chance to own a piece of Sandpoint at an unbeatable price. Here is an option to embrace the freedom of homeownership in this vibrant community.
